casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Richard, Appellant, v. Wells, Judge, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Richard v. Wells (1992), 65 Ohio St.3d 137.]

(No. 92-1358 — Submitted October 13, 1992 — Decided November 18, 1992.) Donald L. Richard, Sr., pro se. *138Stephanie Tubbs Jones, Prosecuting Attorney, and Karen L. Johnson, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
